      "factId": "hz.web.d0fd1e81772d0d1e.fact.4",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "The features available at that site have been replaced as follows: - The interactive tools are now at https://author-tools.ietf.org - The catalog of tools is now at Tools catalog - The xml2rfc vocabulary documentation is now at RFCXML Vocabulary - The repositories for the various tools are now in the ietf-tools organisation on GitHub ¶ Introducing Internet-Drafts Internet-Drafts (I-Ds) are the basic work items of the IETF and they are produced for a variety of purposes by a wide range of individuals and groups.",
